survey_response.review_text: DR NEHA & DR VARUN both had done my treatment they were both very good 👍 excellent 👌 humble will highly recommend to everyone
Friendly atmosphere with superb service. Dr. Neva demonstrated great expertise and was  gentle and friendly during the whole procedure.

Dr Neha is excellent with children! She makes sure they are comfortable at every stage. My son didn't realise he was getting an injection or the forceps were being used because she distracted him throughout. The process was clean, comfortable and reassuring. The clinic is easily reachable off the Eastern Ex Highway. Highly recommend her for kids and adults looking for general dentistry solutions.

It was a really good experience. We learnt many new things about studying in abroad which we are unaware of. Dr Neha and Dr Varun are really humble and they answer all your queries helping you to take decisions about your future studies. I would surely suggest CODE for all students who have sincere doubts about dental studies abroad.

*** **** ****** ** ************* *  compassionate about her job. She treats patients with care & concern for the patients. Her hands work dexterously on her patients' teeth. She is trained in the US & has acquired special skills that are scarce even in a place like Mumbai.
 
I find her work to be hugely effective in solving dental problems of her patients..
Dr. Neha's friendly immediately put me at ease. She was eager to hear about my doubts and solved them with patience
*** ** * **** **** ****** * ** Dr Neha nd her husband Dr Varun from long time.. They ar amazing nd best
The treatment was really good didn't feel any pain or problem had a very good experience. I'm happy with it.
